{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/nueva-carta-en-el-restaurante-portolito-en-la-playa-de-valencia/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"A pizcas y a mizcas"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"4652ae80-0b84-564d-853f-8a9765c91c95","excerpt":"¿Es posible innovar culinariamente cuando tu emplazamiento te condiciona mucho? Al parecer sí, y esta es la apuesta que el restaurante Portolito hace en un…","html":"<p>¿Es posible innovar culinariamente cuando tu emplazamiento te condiciona mucho? Al parecer sí, y esta es la apuesta que el restaurante <a href=\"http://www.portolito.com/\">Portolito</a> hace en un lugar tan emblemático como el Paseo Neptuno (en el número 34), en la playa de Las Arenas de Valencia. Un sitio que automáticamente se vincula a arroces, clótxinas, ensalada valenciana… Su chef, Enrique Campos (también en <a href=\"/cena-en-lotelito/\">Lotelito</a>), ha preparado platos muy interesantes. Os lo contamos.</p>\n<h2>Nuestra comida en restaurante Portolito</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Comida</strong>: <span role=\"img\" aria-label=\"star\">⭐</span><span role=\"img\" aria-label=\"star\">⭐</span><span role=\"img\" aria-label=\"star\">⭐</span></li>\n<li><strong>Local</strong>: <span role=\"img\" aria-label=\"star\">⭐</span><span role=\"img\" aria-label=\"star\">⭐</span><span role=\"img\" aria-label=\"star\">⭐</span><span role=\"img\" aria-label=\"star\">⭐</span></li>\n<li><strong>Servicio</strong>: <span role=\"img\" aria-label=\"star\">⭐</span><span role=\"img\" aria-label=\"star\">⭐</span><span role=\"img\" aria-label=\"star\">⭐</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/8bfac2e848fbe86c09d3e30d33a34902/2d8bb/IMG_20151016_142231-Pizcas.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 96.83544303797468%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"IMG 20151016 142231 Pizcas\"\n        title=\"IMG 20151016 142231 Pizcas\"\n        src=\"/static/8bfac2e848fbe86c09d3e30d33a34902/828fb/IMG_20151016_142231-Pizcas.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/8bfac2e848fbe86c09d3e30d33a34902/ff44c/IMG_20151016_142231-Pizcas.jpg 158w,\n/static/8bfac2e848fbe86c09d3e30d33a34902/a6688/IMG_20151016_142231-Pizcas.jpg 315w,\n/static/8bfac2e848fbe86c09d3e30d33a34902/828fb/IMG_20151016_142231-Pizcas.jpg 630w,\n/static/8bfac2e848fbe86c09d3e30d33a34902/2d8bb/IMG_20151016_142231-Pizcas.jpg 835w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Acudimos, junto con un grupo de periodistas y bloggers gastronómicos a conocer la nueva propuesta gastronómica. La selección que nos presentaron fue la siguiente:</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/922bf5f8b9a74c9ca6d7978301974091/47311/IMG_20151016_141201-Pizcas.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 75.31645569620254%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"IMG 20151016 141201 Pizcas\"\n        title=\"IMG 20151016 141201 Pizcas\"\n        src=\"/static/922bf5f8b9a74c9ca6d7978301974091/828fb/IMG_20151016_141201-Pizcas.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/922bf5f8b9a74c9ca6d7978301974091/ff44c/IMG_20151016_141201-Pizcas.jpg 158w,\n/static/922bf5f8b9a74c9ca6d7978301974091/a6688/IMG_20151016_141201-Pizcas.jpg 315w,\n/static/922bf5f8b9a74c9ca6d7978301974091/828fb/IMG_20151016_141201-Pizcas.jpg 630w,\n/static/922bf5f8b9a74c9ca6d7978301974091/0ede0/IMG_20151016_141201-Pizcas.jpg 945w,\n/static/922bf5f8b9a74c9ca6d7978301974091/47311/IMG_20151016_141201-Pizcas.jpg 1080w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Nueva carta Portolito</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Buñuelo de gambita roja, pescadilla y piquillo</li>\n<li>Pez mantequilla “brasa” con trufa, algas y caviar de wasabi</li>\n<li>Foie con membrillo, queso de cabra y polvo de aceite ahumado</li>\n<li>Cremoso de alcachofas con ajo negro, langostinos y regaliz</li>\n<li>Huevo crujiente con patata al carbón y sopa de ceps y patata</li>\n<li>Albóndigas de rabo de toro con curry verde y especias</li>\n<li>Chocolate con fruta de la pasión y avellanas</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Como véis, una apuesta por ofrecer algo diferente y a precios muy, muy competitivos, para ser el entorno que es. La selección nos pareció fantástica. Y nos encantó el buñuelo de gambita roja, el cremoso de alcachofas y las albóndigas (que traigan más pan para la salsa, jeje). Además, Enrique “improvisó” un arroz marinero que le pedimos y que estuvo riquísimo.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/03e15c39d40855bef813396c2eddbfa9/47311/IMG_20151016_161134-Pizcas.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 75.31645569620254%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"IMG 20151016 161134 Pizcas\"\n        title=\"IMG 20151016 161134 Pizcas\"\n        src=\"/static/03e15c39d40855bef813396c2eddbfa9/828fb/IMG_20151016_161134-Pizcas.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/03e15c39d40855bef813396c2eddbfa9/ff44c/IMG_20151016_161134-Pizcas.jpg 158w,\n/static/03e15c39d40855bef813396c2eddbfa9/a6688/IMG_20151016_161134-Pizcas.jpg 315w,\n/static/03e15c39d40855bef813396c2eddbfa9/828fb/IMG_20151016_161134-Pizcas.jpg 630w,\n/static/03e15c39d40855bef813396c2eddbfa9/0ede0/IMG_20151016_161134-Pizcas.jpg 945w,\n/static/03e15c39d40855bef813396c2eddbfa9/47311/IMG_20151016_161134-Pizcas.jpg 1080w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Arroz marinero</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/b126311c627ca5e2f1337f8c16604254/47311/IMG_20151016_163641-Pizcas.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 75.31645569620254%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"IMG 20151016 163641 Pizcas\"\n        title=\"IMG 20151016 163641 Pizcas\"\n        src=\"/static/b126311c627ca5e2f1337f8c16604254/828fb/IMG_20151016_163641-Pizcas.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/b126311c627ca5e2f1337f8c16604254/ff44c/IMG_20151016_163641-Pizcas.jpg 158w,\n/static/b126311c627ca5e2f1337f8c16604254/a6688/IMG_20151016_163641-Pizcas.jpg 315w,\n/static/b126311c627ca5e2f1337f8c16604254/828fb/IMG_20151016_163641-Pizcas.jpg 630w,\n/static/b126311c627ca5e2f1337f8c16604254/0ede0/IMG_20151016_163641-Pizcas.jpg 945w,\n/static/b126311c627ca5e2f1337f8c16604254/47311/IMG_20151016_163641-Pizcas.jpg 1080w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Tras la agradable comida, llena de risas y de buen rollo, Enrique Campos salió de los fogones y se interesó mucho por conocer nuestras opiniones. Saber escuchar es un gran don que muy poca gente tiene.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/e38bde3837555d092d2c8b05ec06c07f/47311/IMG_20151016_165721-Pizcas.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 75.31645569620254%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"IMG 20151016 165721 Pizcas\"\n        title=\"IMG 20151016 165721 Pizcas\"\n        src=\"/static/e38bde3837555d092d2c8b05ec06c07f/828fb/IMG_20151016_165721-Pizcas.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/e38bde3837555d092d2c8b05ec06c07f/ff44c/IMG_20151016_165721-Pizcas.jpg 158w,\n/static/e38bde3837555d092d2c8b05ec06c07f/a6688/IMG_20151016_165721-Pizcas.jpg 315w,\n/static/e38bde3837555d092d2c8b05ec06c07f/828fb/IMG_20151016_165721-Pizcas.jpg 630w,\n/static/e38bde3837555d092d2c8b05ec06c07f/0ede0/IMG_20151016_165721-Pizcas.jpg 945w,\n/static/e38bde3837555d092d2c8b05ec06c07f/47311/IMG_20151016_165721-Pizcas.jpg 1080w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>","frontmatter":{"title":"Nueva carta en el restaurante Portolito en la playa de Valencia","date":"October 18, 2015","description":null}},"previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/calabaza-asada/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Calabaza asada"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/pasta-con-pulpo-y-tomate/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Pasta con pulpo y tomate"}}},"pageContext":{"id":"4652ae80-0b84-564d-853f-8a9765c91c95","previousPostId":"71189af9-b580-5947-8fe4-f37beed1b580","nextPostId":"845f9430-c015-5024-be54-98ea5bea52c4"}},"staticQueryHashes":["2841359383","3257411868"]}